Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:21.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}掌上的微风 在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:35.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}我已经能用全新的笑容 向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:47.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}尽管回忆溢满心头 我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:57.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无所谓在干掉的泪痕中 有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:10.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}没错 我会以迎接朋友的方式 温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:23.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头 我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:27.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小时候到现在 关于下雨天都没什么好回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学入学典礼那天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远足的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 连初恋的时候也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,要不要一起撑?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说,我最喜欢下雨天了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很合得来耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两千圆还我好不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里碰到你真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,这样啊,没钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你代替我点名 我就少收你一点,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四点开始的语言学喔 就拜托你罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的帮了我一个大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 下雨的日子我总是很倒楣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#17 响子的初恋故事 总是在下雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该早点出来才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…一起撑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你是…七尾?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,你帮了我一个大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的,反正我很闲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋,要聊些什么好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代在学校吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,应该傍晚就会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都这么早就回来啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想看 星期一和星期三是傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期二和星期五是八点左右
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期四要打工当家教 十点才会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六就不一定了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么这么清楚呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该怎么说呢 因为我是管理员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是因为这个缘故吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,你对其他房客的作息 也掌握得这么清楚吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然罗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也不见得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员真的好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接回家不要乱跑喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一郎,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,把你的裙子弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请到我家清洗一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一留下痕迹就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么麻烦啦,真的没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙子干之前 请你先穿我的裙子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,腰身好紧喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我泡茶给你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么客气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话题,话题…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得五代怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?你是指什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们经常在一起啊 你觉得他是个怎么样的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很难用一句话来形容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还有其他交往的女生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道耶,好像只有你一个而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是时钟坡第二中学毕业的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩话题转得好快喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代跟我那时的初恋情人 长得很像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初恋情人?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我单方面爱慕他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人很有趣吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个很棒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是跟五代很像会有多棒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有男子气概,而且很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪里像了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他吃营养午餐的时候 总是最晚吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么跟什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的男朋友很帅耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们第一次见面时 跟你在一起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,三鹰? 他只是普通的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有男朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原…原来你是个寡妇?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我好像问了不该问的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,让我想起他了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他也是我的初恋情人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(音无老师在外面喔)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先回去吧,我还有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,每次碰到音无老师的事 她就像失了魂似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说,又是那个音无老师?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,她说要和他一起撑伞回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种老头子有什么好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,进来一起撑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是三班的同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,我叫千草响子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千草同学 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷吧,小心会感冒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前做的事还蛮有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我还以为这招很高明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校的老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,他只是个兼职的讲师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟初恋情人结婚对吧 好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看你高中时代的相簿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相簿?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也突然觉得很怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到五代回来为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那么就看到他回来为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等雨小一点再回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有点晚了,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常这个时候已经回来了说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的相簿很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空再来玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候好年轻喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是变装大会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一郎真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音无夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎么现在才回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小津江等到刚刚才走耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!她到这里来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,打个电话给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直等到刚刚才走耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫…叫我打电话给她?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,为什么呢?真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她又不是那种关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了,我才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用打什么电话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又不是那种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,他在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,一之濑太太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,进来进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,小津江吗?是我,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你今天来找我? 有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,这样啊,那明天见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课?我会翘课啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,没关系,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他居然说那种话耶,你很嫉妒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁嫉妒啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我挂罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟个笨蛋似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,这把伞还给小津江
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天她忘了带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,我要去上学…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是今天要翘课 去跟小津江见面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我跟她又不是那种关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事没什么好偷偷摸摸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小津江会很失望的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会破坏 她的初恋情人的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可以说吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么事? 什么初恋情人的形象?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小津江说你很像她的初恋情人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 原来我不是她的初恋情人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是个很棒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是个很棒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要光明正大一点 这也是为了小津江啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了小津江要光明正大一点?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不了解人家的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,她明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事 上次她明明还为了小津江的事吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么! 你知道我初恋情人的事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,你有在生气吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要生气?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被当作别的男生的替身 总会不舒服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我也希望 你能正视眼前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,我有正视你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说 管理员是个很棒的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天她说了她老公的事给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨天的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那是她的初恋情人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的好专情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么温文儒雅的响子 居然会做出这种惊人之举…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定很爱他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕喔 可以跟心爱的人结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,他已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你不要死喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要你死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在胡说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真是痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一种受不了的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来一郎 还活在她的心里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子真是太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对死去的人念念不忘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.65,0:21:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么她就不肯多看我一眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来一起撑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,我想一个人走路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.89,0:22:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,感冒了怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.56,0:22:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在闹什么别扭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,都不明白人家的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,她明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,总有一天,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.10,0:23:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,还是借我撑一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间过得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.14,0:23:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到一刻馆 已经要迎接第二次的圣诞节了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,这是我的一点心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:23:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“响子的礼物 咦!这个要送给我?”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.85,0:24:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我用心编织的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.36,0:24:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:06.38,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.13,0:24:34.48,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}那天在陌生的城市下了一场阵雨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.51,0:24:41.19,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}你非常在意淋湿的高跟鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.22,0:24:49.41,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}从前你用那隐藏着 稚气的侧脸和我交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.44,0:24:55.50,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}你说的话语至今仍能想起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.53,0:25:03.30,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}一开始就仿佛 置身电影中的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.33,0:25:11.97,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}你轻声细语地说着 安静的最后一幕

